You need to rebuilt your kernel using this mtrr.patch in order to build NVidia 304.131

go to /usr/src/linux-4.4
patch -p1 < /path/to/mtrr.patch
cp /boot/config-generic-smp-4.4-smp .config
make oldconfig
make bzImage
cp arch/x86/boot/bzImage /boot/vmlinuz-generic-smp-4.4-smp
/sbin/lilo -v
reboot

After that, you can reinstall NVidia driver again.
